            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Worst school to ever exist. Old SFS was actually thriving and not money-minded; however, since this new principal joined, things have turned for the worse. They only care about money. Teachers are extremely unprofessional and give low marks to students because of their personal grudges and they don't even show the answer sheets. They don't know how to conduct PTMs. During the final term's PTM, my ward and I didn't even get the chance to speak to the teacher one-on-one, and we weren't allowed to meet any subject teachers either. Some teachers are actually amazing and sweet, while many teachers are so unprofessional that they objectify girls, character assassinate children, and spread rumours. There is no sense of privacy for the child in this school; they WILL check your ward's personal messages and pictures on the phones. They mostly post pictures and videos of the junior wing, as it is very big and pretty, but often hide the reality. Please don't ruin your child's mental health by admitting your ward to this school. ",
